  <scopecontent id="aspace_38a6d638c46fbe1b8cc7c3801f36c495">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Paper ephemera, postcards, and photographs related to the Brooklyn Bridge and other New York landmarks. Includes booklet, program, invitation, and ticket to opening ceremony for bridge on May 24, 1883. Also includes receipt for the purchase of Randall's Island, as well as miscellany related to the Holland Tunnel and the Statue of Liberty.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <arrangement id="aspace_cf48e517901659fa9d28961af57162e3">
